Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:01:57.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}GO CRY GO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:09.54,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Where is the truths
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:12.05,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}今無情一帯の世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:14.16,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Here is no truths
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.31,0:02:16.67,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}栄光もなく奪い合う
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:19.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}It's like a party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:21.51,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}交錯する者たちよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:23.73,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}突き進め果てるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.73,0:02:25.41,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}勝者と敗者どちらも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:26.54,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}maybe something crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:28.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}What can I belive?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:31.36,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}そんな問いなんで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:33.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}No one answer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.64,0:02:39.69,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}すべてこの虚空の中消えてった
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:44.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}今はBREAK OUT BREAK OUT進めよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.38,0:02:45.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:50.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}その意志を揚げて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:53.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}さあもっとBREAK OUT BREAK OUT世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:55.12,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.12,0:03:00.42,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}切り開け迷っても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:03.07,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}So we gatta just go crazy,crazy and mad
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:04.83,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}just go crazy now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.82,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}dance,dance crazy ,crazy and mad
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:10.56,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}夢か地獄かGO CRY GO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:01:57.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}GO CRY GO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:09.54,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真理何處尋覓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:12.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}眼前這冷酷無情的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:14.16,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}真理無從尋覓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.31,0:02:16.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}僅有骯髒的搶與奪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:19.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}就像一場派對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:21.51,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}命運縱橫交錯的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:23.73,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}向著終點一意前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.73,0:02:25.41,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}無論勝者或敗者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:26.54,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}或許某物已然瘋狂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:28.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}何物可信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:31.36,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}如此疑問為何…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.36,0:02:33.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}無人作答
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.64,0:02:39.69,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}一切盡皆消失在這片虛無之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:44.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}現在BREAK OUT BREAK OUT  前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.38,0:02:45.64,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:50.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}高舉這份決心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:53.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}來吧  繼續BREAK OUT BREAK OUT突破
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.86,0:02:55.12,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}CRY OUT CRY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.12,0:03:00.42,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}世界的束縛  即使迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:03.07,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我們只需變得瘋狂  瘋而狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:04.83,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}如今只需變得瘋狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.82,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}舞蹈  舞至瘋狂  瘋而狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:10.56,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}夢或地獄  GO CRY GO
